
HTML - Markup lang for structure and content
CSS - Styling of my content
Javascript - what happens when you do something with the structure.

Its possible to right desktop applications in JS liek any other programmin lang.

JS works only inside another app. Eg: Inside web browser. All browsers have the js engine inside it

OS -> Web browser -> page -> JS 

JS doesnt have the access to local files.
Cant directly access DB
Cant access hardware

JS - Client side pgm lang where code is executed on client browser after interpreting html and css recieved.
     unlike server side programs which execue code on the web servers.


